1
00:01:52,870 --> 00:01:53,870
If it were poisoned,

2
00:01:53,870 --> 00:01:55,800
I would be the first to be poisoned.

3
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:57,130
Then let me ask you,

4
00:01:58,229 --> 00:02:00,280
what about that string of Zhuyao?

5
00:02:11,590 --> 00:02:13,280
I really didn't eat it.

6
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,400
But that is our custom in Changmo.

7
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,240
When I brought it to you,

8
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,840
it had been washed clean.

9
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:23,040
There was nothing wrong with it.

10
00:02:24,430 --> 00:02:24,910
Your Majesty.

11
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:25,510
All right.

12
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:29,280
All right.

13
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,470
I can suspect anyone,

14
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:33,470
but I

15
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:36,800
can't suspect my own Consort Ling.

16
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,240
You look haggard.

17
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,680
You must have...

18
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:47,280
worried about my health lately.

19
00:02:49,590 --> 00:02:50,960
Let me help you rest.

20
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:51,590
I'm...

21
00:02:51,590 --> 00:02:52,360
not tired.

22
00:03:13,030 --> 00:03:13,750
Let me

23
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:15,680
tuck you in.

24
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:18,480
Your Majesty, aren't you going to rest?

25
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,400
I want to watch you sleep.

26
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,120
Your Majesty,

27
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:26,360
I have something important to report.

28
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:29,520
You get some rest first.

29
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,970
I will be right back.

30
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:43,590
Your Majesty,

31
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:45,800
what you wanted to investigate
is now clear.

32
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,560
Huo Ran was indeed

33
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,870
planted by the late Emperor
by Lord Fei's side

34
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:51,190
to keep an eye on him.

35
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:54,590
What did Huo Ran say?

36
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:57,400
He said everything was fine before,

37
00:03:57,430 --> 00:03:58,310
but

38
00:03:58,310 --> 00:04:00,750
ever since he came back
from Tianlang Pass,

39
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:03,190
Lord Fei has been acting a little strange.

40
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:05,800
Okay.

41
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,080
Got it.

42
00:04:15,150 --> 00:04:15,950
Your Majesty,

43
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:18,630
aren't you going back to Consort Ling?

44
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,690
With someone beside me,

45
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,630
I can't sleep well.

46
00:04:41,950 --> 00:04:42,750
Jin Xi.

47
00:04:44,270 --> 00:04:45,070
Jin Xi.

48
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:50,070
Hall Master.

49
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,390
If she doesn't take the antidote soon,

50
00:04:52,390 --> 00:04:53,450
she won't survive.

51
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,630
What did you say?

52
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:59,000
Please grant her the antidote,
Hall Master.

53
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,659
Otherwise,

54
00:04:59,830 --> 00:05:01,630
she won't even last half an hour.

55
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:03,000
No rush.

56
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:05,270
I want you to watch her

57
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:08,430
suffer the consequences
of disobeying my orders.

58
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:09,870
Does it pain you?

59
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,190
Pain me?

60
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:16,870
She lives

61
00:05:17,830 --> 00:05:18,830
merely because she remains useful

62
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:19,830
in the palace.

63
00:05:20,270 --> 00:05:21,120
Otherwise,

64
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,280
if I were by Liu Chu's side alone,

65
00:05:23,830 --> 00:05:25,630
I couldn't hold everything together.

66
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:27,000
Now, you look a bit

67
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,120
like a Changmo spy.

68
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:30,950
Don't worry.

69
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,480
I won't let her die.

70
00:05:32,830 --> 00:05:34,480
When your poison acts up,

71
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,560
I'll have her watch you the same way.

72
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:43,950
Hand over the real antidote.

73
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,430
Do it.

74
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:47,600
Kill me.

75
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,060
You think I wouldn't dare?

76
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,560
Kill me,

77
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:54,760
and no one can control you two anymore.

78
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:55,830
Oh, right,

79
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:59,090
and no one will give you
the antidote anymore.

80
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,680
Then you two will hold each other,

81
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:03,750
suffering a fate worse than death.

82
00:06:03,750 --> 00:06:06,010
Just thinking about it makes me so happy.

83
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,480
I have lain hidden in Jinglan

84
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,750
for so many years.

85
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:24,750
I don't even remember

86
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:26,160
how much I've suffered.

87
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,160
Now I am atop all ministerial ranks.

88
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:28,950
But you?

89
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,010
You have never shown up.

90
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,000
I am human too.

91
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,480
So what?

92
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,480
You will always be a pawn of Changmo.

93
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,630
I have never forgotten my identity.

94
00:06:39,390 --> 00:06:40,680
For all these years,

95
00:06:40,830 --> 00:06:41,870
in all I do,

96
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,960
I have taken Changmo's
grand mission as my own.

97
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:50,870
So I beg you, Hall Master,
to grant me the antidote,

98
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,510
so Jin Xi

99
00:06:53,390 --> 00:06:54,870
can lend me a hand.

100
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,070
She is my subordinate.

101
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,900
I naturally won't let her die.

102
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,750
But when your poison acts up,

103
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:06,240
whether you can find me

104
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,160
depends on your luck.

105
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:12,200
Thank you, Hall Master.

106
00:07:12,630 --> 00:07:13,430
You may leave.

107
00:07:13,870 --> 00:07:14,480
Yes.

108
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,800
He has feelings for you.

109
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,950
Then it seems

110
00:07:23,950 --> 00:07:25,350
you are still of some use.

111
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:35,920
It's useless.

112
00:07:36,950 --> 00:07:38,610
Even if he has feelings for me,

113
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,190
it's useless.

114
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,570
Whether it's useful or not,

115
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,560
we'll know once we try.

116
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,070
Lord Zhang.

117
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,070
How are you today?

118
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:02,410
I've been waiting for so long,

119
00:08:02,630 --> 00:08:04,750
and you've finally come.

120
00:08:05,390 --> 00:08:06,990
How did you know I would come?

121
00:08:07,070 --> 00:08:08,630
I thought

122
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:10,830
His Majesty would remember our old ties

123
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:14,000
and come to see me one last time.

124
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:16,870
I didn't expect it to be you.

125
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,680
It's good that it's you.

126
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:20,390
Now that you are here,

127
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,750
I can finally drink this pot of wine

128
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:27,510
with peace of mind.

129
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:34,240
Thank you for visiting me.

130
00:08:39,270 --> 00:08:40,240
Lord Zhang.

131
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,669
You ending up like this

132
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,240
is entirely your own doing.

133
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:47,960
General Xiao,

134
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:51,360
do you really think I would
secretly keep a dragon robe?

135
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:54,440
Do you really think I would rebel?

136
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,360
Actually,

137
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:59,030
His Majesty knows everything.

138
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:01,080
Li Shichang

139
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,670
is framing me up.

140
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:05,390
Then why would His Majesty punish you?

141
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,840
Because His Majesty has grown up,

142
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:15,960
and he doesn't need me anymore.

143
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:18,150
And these trumped-up charges

144
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:21,360
are the best excuse to get rid of me.

145
00:09:21,670 --> 00:09:23,030
General Xiao,

146
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:24,630
you are smart and wise.

147
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,360
How could you not know?

148
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,080
Why bother asking?

149
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:31,610
Even if you had no intention to rebel,

150
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:32,750
Lord Zhang,

151
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:35,150
how do you explain

152
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,840
the Huangpi Village incident?

153
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,670
So the annihilation

154
00:09:38,670 --> 00:09:40,600
of my entire family

155
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:43,360
has atoned for their lives.

156
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:46,870
Even if there's a slight risk,

157
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:50,150
I couldn't let the tragedy
from 8 years ago

158
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:52,080
happen again.

159
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:56,390
Eight years ago?

160
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:05,030
General Xiao.

161
00:10:05,670 --> 00:10:08,000
A strange disease 8 years ago

162
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,670
turned the whole Jinglan

163
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:12,030
into a living hell.

164
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,320
My son

165
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:16,670
also caught the disease.

166
00:10:17,390 --> 00:10:20,520
Although the Han family
tried their best to save people,

167
00:10:21,030 --> 00:10:23,600
many still died.

168
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:25,960
Finally, the disease stabilized.

169
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:28,200
I thought my son

170
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,600
could survive.

171
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:31,910
Unexpectedly,

172
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:35,890
after taking a dose of medicine
from the Han family,

173
00:10:36,670 --> 00:10:38,870
he suddenly died.

174
00:10:39,750 --> 00:10:40,630
So,

175
00:10:41,270 --> 00:10:43,530
you hated the Han family because of this.

176
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:46,740
Han Yunling was in danger several times.

177
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,200
Lord Zhang,

178
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:50,110
it was all your doing, right?

179
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:52,030
That's right.

180
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,240
It was me.

181
00:10:55,030 --> 00:10:56,030
From the moment Han Yunling

182
00:10:56,030 --> 00:10:58,080
stepped into Jinglan,

183
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:01,870
I sent people
to assassinate her every day.

184
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:02,840
If it weren't for you,

185
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:05,870
I would have avenged my son long ago.

186
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:08,630
But the prescription
was not written by Han Yunling.

187
00:11:08,630 --> 00:11:09,440
Lord Zhang,

188
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,240
she is innocent.

189
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,870
What about my son?

190
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:15,390
How innocent was he!

191
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,360
I also know

192
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:24,870
I can't entirely blame the Han family.

193
00:11:25,870 --> 00:11:26,960
But I

194
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:30,440
only had this one son.

195
00:11:33,270 --> 00:11:33,790
I...

196
00:11:37,270 --> 00:11:40,270
I have hatred in my heart!

197
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,480
I hate them!

198
00:11:52,030 --> 00:11:53,270
When

199
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:54,670
I was young,

200
00:11:55,030 --> 00:11:58,230
I followed the late Emperor
in campaigns across the land.

201
00:11:58,360 --> 00:12:00,270
After the late Emperor passed away,

202
00:12:00,270 --> 00:12:02,870
I've devoted myself
to assisting His Majesty,

203
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:05,000
fulfilling my duties

204
00:12:05,030 --> 00:12:06,960
and serving the people wholeheartedly.

205
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,630
With my assistance,

206
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:11,240
Jinglan has become even more prosperous.

207
00:12:11,630 --> 00:12:13,360
If annihilating the Han family

208
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:15,890
is me abusing my power for personal gain,

209
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,080
then

210
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:20,600
I'll own this one and only stain

211
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:23,200
on my life.

212
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:28,660
Lord Zhang.

213
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,150
General Xiao.

214
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:33,150
Do you know who sent you

215
00:12:33,390 --> 00:12:36,080
to Tianlang Pass back then?

216
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,630
It was me.

217
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:42,030
When Changmo attacked with a massive army,

218
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:44,080
Tianlang Pass was on the verge of falling.

219
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,390
The frontline desperately needed a capable

220
00:12:45,390 --> 00:12:47,600
and loyal military general.

221
00:12:47,670 --> 00:12:48,870
You and Fei Zheng

222
00:12:49,030 --> 00:12:51,000
were both close to His Majesty.

223
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:53,390
Fei Zheng was also very capable.

224
00:12:54,030 --> 00:12:55,750
But I always felt

225
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:57,960
that Fei Zheng

226
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:01,150
harbored an unspeakable secret.

227
00:13:01,670 --> 00:13:03,360
So I resolutely

228
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,670
sent you.

229
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:07,440
You indeed did not let me down.

230
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:08,790
However,

231
00:13:09,790 --> 00:13:12,390
your interference
in the Han family's affairs

232
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:15,960
forced me to eliminate you.

233
00:13:18,550 --> 00:13:19,440
So it seems

234
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:22,000
the poisoned dart incident
in Huangpi Village

235
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,270
was also your doing.

236
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:24,670
That's right.

237
00:13:25,750 --> 00:13:26,870
It was me.

238
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:36,550
It is all over.

239
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:46,750
Seeing you and Fei Zheng
build your careers

240
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:48,680
and receive great imperial grace,

241
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:52,870
I think of my dead son.

242
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:56,030
If he were still alive,

243
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:59,030
he would be just like you,

244
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:04,360
a pillar of Jinglan,

245
00:14:05,670 --> 00:14:06,870
wouldn't he?

246
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:09,660
Lord Zhang.

247
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,370
Let me have a drink with you.

248
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,150
General Xiao,

249
00:14:16,670 --> 00:14:17,870
thank you.

250
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:21,870
Thank you for coming to see me today.

251
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:25,670
Only I am qualified

252
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:30,270
to drink

253
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,200
this pot of wine.

254
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:35,240
Son,

255
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:40,030
we will meet soon anyway.

256
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:43,330
Lord Zhang.

257
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:45,870
Lord Zhang!

258
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,080
Lord Zhang!

259
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,240
Lord Zhang.

260
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:51,240
Guards!

261
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:54,790
General Xiao,

262
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:57,750
remember this.

263
00:14:57,870 --> 00:14:58,840
His Majesty

264
00:14:59,510 --> 00:15:00,910
has become

265
00:15:00,910 --> 00:15:03,440
a meticulous emperor.

266
00:15:04,150 --> 00:15:06,030
When serving an emperor,

267
00:15:06,630 --> 00:15:08,360
men may easily share hardship,

268
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:10,840
but not

269
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:12,870
prosperity.

270
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,240
Lord Zhang.

271
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:15,790
Lord Zhang.

272
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,440
Why must you do this?

273
00:15:19,030 --> 00:15:20,670
I prided myself all my life

274
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:23,750
on being upright and innocent.

275
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:27,960
But I have also done many wrong things.

276
00:15:28,870 --> 00:15:31,870
Even if His Majesty granted me mercy,

277
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:35,480
I would have no desire...

278
00:15:37,630 --> 00:15:38,440
Lord Zhang.

279
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,000
Guards!

280
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,080
To stay...

281
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:49,480
to stay in this world.

282
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:53,550
Lord Zhang.

283
00:15:53,910 --> 00:15:54,870
Lord Zhang.

284
00:15:55,670 --> 00:15:57,030
Guards!

285
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:02,270
Physician Han Yunling,

286
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:03,870
with her sincere heart

287
00:16:03,870 --> 00:16:05,480
and exquisite skills,

288
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:07,870
is truly a model for physicians.

289
00:16:08,030 --> 00:16:10,390
She is hereby awarded 100 taels of gold

290
00:16:10,390 --> 00:16:12,240
and 10 bolts of brocade

291
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:14,030
to honor her contributions.

292
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:16,240
Thus decreed.

293
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,630
Thank you for the reward, Your Majesty.

294
00:16:19,630 --> 00:16:21,790
I only did my duty as a physician.

295
00:16:22,630 --> 00:16:23,360
You may rise.

296
00:16:23,870 --> 00:16:25,270
Thank you, Your Majesty.

297
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:28,200
Fei Zheng has served at court
for many years,

298
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:29,960
diligently fulfilling his duties

299
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:32,270
and promoting etiquette.

300
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:33,670
From now on,

301
00:16:33,790 --> 00:16:35,440
Fei Zheng is relieved of his post

302
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:37,600
as Minister of Revenue

303
00:16:37,630 --> 00:16:39,600
and appointed as Minister of Rites

304
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:41,840
to focus on managing
the Ministry of Rites.

305
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:43,670
Thus decreed.

306
00:16:47,030 --> 00:16:48,160
I accept the decree.

307
00:16:49,270 --> 00:16:51,960
The affairs of the Ministry of Rites
are complex.

308
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:55,000
From now on, just focus on
managing the Ministry of Rites.

309
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:55,670
I believe

310
00:16:56,270 --> 00:16:58,480
you will convince all the officials.

311
00:17:01,390 --> 00:17:03,240
-Your Majesty, you're wise.
-Your Majesty, you're wise.

312
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:05,770
-We bow in admiration.
-We bow in admiration.

313
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:09,569
Gold and silver,

314
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:10,790
properties,

315
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:13,880
and taxes from the border fiefs.

316
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:30,030
Logically speaking,

317
00:17:30,030 --> 00:17:32,030
Your Majesty, since you just
recovered from a serious illness

318
00:17:32,030 --> 00:17:34,240
and eliminated hidden dangers
in the court,

319
00:17:34,240 --> 00:17:35,960
rewarding these meritorious officials

320
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:36,880
is inevitable.

321
00:17:37,270 --> 00:17:40,240
However,
regarding the taxes of border fiefs...

322
00:17:42,440 --> 00:17:44,400
there has never been such a system.

323
00:17:45,350 --> 00:17:46,440
Xie,

324
00:17:47,030 --> 00:17:48,480
Fei Zheng and Xiao Chi

325
00:17:49,030 --> 00:17:51,290
are not only retainers who grew up with me

326
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,440
but also important officials in the court

327
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:54,790
that I must rely on.

328
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:57,000
How can I not give them more rewards?

329
00:17:57,030 --> 00:17:57,920
What's more,

330
00:17:58,310 --> 00:18:00,240
Han Yunling even saved my life.

331
00:18:01,030 --> 00:18:03,480
If it were you who got sick,

332
00:18:04,030 --> 00:18:04,640
what

333
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:06,400
would you do?

334
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:10,550
If I were the one sick,

335
00:18:11,070 --> 00:18:13,400
rewarding this much silver
would be enough.

336
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:15,270
But they saved you, Your Majesty.

337
00:18:17,480 --> 00:18:19,350
They must be heavily rewarded.

338
00:18:19,830 --> 00:18:20,480
Very well.

339
00:18:20,790 --> 00:18:21,640
Tomorrow,

340
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:23,680
I will have someone take these things

341
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:25,160
out of the treasury

342
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,200
and send them over.

343
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:29,240
As for the taxes from the border fiefs,

344
00:18:29,830 --> 00:18:31,880
we can only wait
until after the autumn harvest

345
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:33,590
to escort the silver back to the capital.

346
00:18:33,590 --> 00:18:34,680
Only after it enters the treasury

347
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,280
can we give further rewards.

348
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:37,690
Alright.

349
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:40,000
I'll listen to you, Xie.

350
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:41,560
By the way,

351
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:43,050
for all these years,

352
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:45,830
I've known nothing about the treasury.

353
00:18:45,830 --> 00:18:46,790
Xie,

354
00:18:46,790 --> 00:18:48,880
could you give me the treasury ledgers

355
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:49,790
to take a look?

356
00:18:53,270 --> 00:18:55,480
You used to be completely uninterested

357
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:57,480
in these things.

358
00:18:57,880 --> 00:18:58,790
Today...

359
00:19:01,070 --> 00:19:02,480
what has gotten into you?

360
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:04,830
As a ruler,

361
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:06,920
I should be familiar with

362
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:08,800
all the affairs of the state.

363
00:19:09,270 --> 00:19:11,600
After all, they are the treasury ledgers.

364
00:19:11,750 --> 00:19:12,880
And I remember,

365
00:19:13,310 --> 00:19:15,170
when our father was on the throne,

366
00:19:15,590 --> 00:19:17,160
he seemed never to have handed

367
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:18,360
the treasury ledgers

368
00:19:18,590 --> 00:19:19,640
to anyone else,

369
00:19:20,030 --> 00:19:20,640
right?

370
00:19:22,510 --> 00:19:23,160
Yes.

371
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:29,400
Our father was a wise and valiant man.

372
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:31,070
Back then,

373
00:19:31,070 --> 00:19:32,590
he executed the brothers
who fought alongside him

374
00:19:32,590 --> 00:19:34,240
to conquer the empire

375
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:36,480
just to secure his throne.

376
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:47,020
I don't know about these things, Xie.

377
00:19:47,310 --> 00:19:48,570
I was still young then.

378
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:49,720
You must know

379
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:51,850
these situations better than I do.

380
00:19:52,160 --> 00:19:53,510
I just want

381
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:55,270
to learn about the ledgers.

382
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:56,480
Xie,

383
00:19:56,830 --> 00:19:58,360
please don't overthink it.

384
00:19:58,790 --> 00:19:59,750
Of course not.

385
00:20:00,550 --> 00:20:01,510
Tomorrow, I will have someone

386
00:20:01,510 --> 00:20:03,200
send the treasury ledgers
from all these years

387
00:20:03,200 --> 00:20:04,270
to you.

388
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:04,790
Really?

389
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:08,590
You still don't trust me.

390
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:10,640
How could I not trust you?

391
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:12,880
You are the person I trust the most.

392
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:14,400
Xie,

393
00:20:14,550 --> 00:20:16,030
my ear is itching again.

394
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:18,070
Could you give me an ear cleaning?

395
00:20:19,270 --> 00:20:20,000
Sure.

396
00:20:20,350 --> 00:20:21,400
Bring the tools.

397
00:20:30,510 --> 00:20:31,110
Oh, right.

398
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:33,030
I just remembered.

399
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:36,640
I haven't had my afternoon medicine yet.

400
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:37,900
If I don't go back soon,

401
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:40,790
the poison in my body might act up again.

402
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:41,960
Then I will

403
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:42,880
take my leave.

404
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:57,880
Are we really going
to send the ledgers over?

405
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:01,410
Today, he wants to see the ledgers.

406
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:04,880
Tomorrow, he will want
to take back the treasury keys.

407
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:06,750
First it was Wang Ruhai.

408
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:08,030
Then it was Lord Zhang.

409
00:21:08,270 --> 00:21:10,070
Now, even Fei Zheng, close to him,

410
00:21:10,070 --> 00:21:13,400
has been transferred
to a sinecure in the Ministry of Rites.

411
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:16,000
And

412
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:18,030
the ruthlessness in his eyes

413
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:21,960
is just like our father's back then.

414
00:21:25,550 --> 00:21:26,200
Then,

415
00:21:26,510 --> 00:21:27,200
we...

416
00:21:27,790 --> 00:21:29,240
He killed key ministers

417
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:32,590
and seized power.

418
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:35,400
It seems Liu Chu

419
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:37,260
is completely out of control now.

420
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:40,270
Rather than await death,

421
00:21:41,960 --> 00:21:43,640
I must strike first.

422
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:47,940
Notify Xieying Guard.

423
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:50,540
Tomorrow at the Princess's Mansion,

424
00:21:51,310 --> 00:21:53,370
I will host a banquet for His Majesty.

425
00:21:55,680 --> 00:21:56,480
Yes.

426
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:00,880
You're here.

427
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:04,550
What's wrong?

428
00:22:04,550 --> 00:22:05,880
Something on your mind?

429
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:10,960
Lord Zhang is dead.

430
00:22:13,790 --> 00:22:16,400
Didn't he deserve it?

431
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:19,060
Although we didn't get along,

432
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:20,880
I only now realize

433
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:23,440
he wasn't actually a bad person.

434
00:22:23,640 --> 00:22:24,720
He was even

435
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:26,980
an indispensable minister in the court.

436
00:22:27,240 --> 00:22:28,830
Even though he was a stubborn old man,

437
00:22:28,830 --> 00:22:30,430
he was devoted to the country

438
00:22:30,510 --> 00:22:31,440
and His Majesty.

439
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:35,040
Then why did he
secretly keep a dragon robe?

440
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:36,750
He didn't explain.

441
00:22:37,070 --> 00:22:38,070
But I feel like

442
00:22:38,590 --> 00:22:40,320
it's not something he would do.

443
00:22:42,350 --> 00:22:43,590
He's dead anyway.

444
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:45,400
Don't overthink it.

445
00:22:46,750 --> 00:22:47,590
Yeah.

446
00:22:48,590 --> 00:22:49,680
He is dead.

447
00:22:50,070 --> 00:22:51,240
All past grievances

448
00:22:51,830 --> 00:22:53,230
should come to an end too.

449
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:06,000
About what happened back then,

450
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:08,130
do you really remember nothing at all?

451
00:23:11,590 --> 00:23:13,320
It seems the old saying is true.

452
00:23:15,400 --> 00:23:16,400
What old saying?

453
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:19,290
"A physician can't heal themselves."

454
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:21,790
You even know that.

455
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:26,010
Since a physician can't heal themselves,

456
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:28,660
I'll find someone to heal you.

457
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:39,830
Physician Han, your pulse is stable.

458
00:23:39,830 --> 00:23:41,270
It shows no abnormalities.

459
00:23:41,270 --> 00:23:43,790
As for the memory loss you mentioned,

460
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:45,680
there is nothing I can do.

461
00:23:58,030 --> 00:23:58,830
Physician.

462
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:01,420
Will this really work?

463
00:24:03,790 --> 00:24:05,520
Have you remembered anything?

464
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:15,000
Then...

465
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:16,750
I'm out of ideas.

466
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:18,200
Hurry up and come out.

467
00:24:26,590 --> 00:24:27,400
Han Yunling.

468
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:29,070
Spirits of heaven.

469
00:24:29,350 --> 00:24:31,160
Spirits of heaven and earth.

470
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,920
Ancestor Bodhisattva, please manifest.

471
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:34,590
Please manifest.

472
00:24:38,550 --> 00:24:39,550
You actually believe this?

473
00:24:39,550 --> 00:24:40,830
Just giving it a try.

474
00:24:41,480 --> 00:24:43,030
Spirits of heaven and earth.

475
00:24:43,030 --> 00:24:45,360
Ancestor Bodhisattva, please manifest.

476
00:24:45,440 --> 00:24:46,720
Please manifest.

477
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:52,400
Chu.

478
00:24:55,790 --> 00:24:56,590
Your Majesty.

479
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:00,790
Zheng, you're here.

480
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:03,350
There are no outsiders here.

481
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:05,030
Why the formal greeting?

482
00:25:05,030 --> 00:25:05,920
Please, rise.

483
00:25:06,270 --> 00:25:06,880
Yes.

484
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:10,830
I asked you to manage
the Ministry of Rites earlier.

485
00:25:10,830 --> 00:25:11,960
Do you have any objections?

486
00:25:11,960 --> 00:25:13,640
It was your arrangement.

487
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:15,640
Naturally, I will obey.

488
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:18,270
Besides, the Ministry of Revenue

489
00:25:18,480 --> 00:25:19,880
is full of tedious tasks.

490
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:21,860
I have long thought of resigning.

491
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:24,480
Good.

492
00:25:26,480 --> 00:25:27,610
Rites and etiquette

493
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:30,030
are Jinglan's dignity.

494
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:32,260
I can't trust anyone else with it.

495
00:25:32,590 --> 00:25:33,990
Only by trusting it to you

496
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:35,880
can I feel at ease.

497
00:25:37,030 --> 00:25:38,000
I will keep

498
00:25:38,270 --> 00:25:40,270
your words in mind.

499
00:25:43,270 --> 00:25:44,680
I just remembered.

500
00:25:45,030 --> 00:25:46,790
Before you came to the Prince's Mansion,

501
00:25:46,790 --> 00:25:49,120
you were a hunter in the mountains, right?

502
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:52,660
In a few days, when we are free,

503
00:25:52,750 --> 00:25:55,080
you and Xiao Chi
will accompany me to hunt.

504
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:00,960
Yes.

505
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:02,880
My father was indeed

506
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:04,480
the best hunter in the village.

507
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:05,440
It's a pity

508
00:26:05,960 --> 00:26:07,440
that he passed away too early.

509
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:09,700
I didn't manage to learn hunting skills.

510
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:13,400
After your father died,

511
00:26:13,550 --> 00:26:15,550
did you enter the Prince's Mansion?

512
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,800
After my father passed away,

513
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:19,790
I was helpless

514
00:26:19,790 --> 00:26:21,320
and ended up on the streets.

515
00:26:21,550 --> 00:26:23,480
Later, I was abducted
by human traffickers.

516
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:24,480
But fortunately,

517
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:26,750
I was sold to the Prince's Mansion.

518
00:26:26,750 --> 00:26:27,830
That's how I met you

519
00:26:27,830 --> 00:26:28,640
and Chi.

520
00:26:31,790 --> 00:26:33,270
Zheng.

521
00:26:35,270 --> 00:26:36,030
Look,

522
00:26:36,640 --> 00:26:37,880
you and Xiao Chi

523
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:40,100
both came from poor backgrounds.

524
00:26:40,680 --> 00:26:41,480
But now?

525
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:43,680
One is the Minister of Rites,

526
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:46,200
and the other is a provincial viceroy.

527
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:49,750
And you are as close as my own brothers.

528
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:53,030
What a great story.

529
00:26:53,550 --> 00:26:56,270
It will surely be recorded
in the history books,

530
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:58,160
praised by everyone,

531
00:26:58,640 --> 00:27:00,500
and passed down for generations.

532
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:04,940
You are absolutely right.

533
00:27:06,030 --> 00:27:07,000
That I

534
00:27:07,510 --> 00:27:08,710
can be where I am today

535
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:11,810
is all thanks to your cultivation.

536
00:27:18,790 --> 00:27:19,590
Your Majesty,

537
00:27:19,790 --> 00:27:21,590
tomorrow is the 15th of September,

538
00:27:21,590 --> 00:27:22,550
the night of the full moon.

539
00:27:22,550 --> 00:27:23,720
Her Highness is going to host a banquet

540
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:25,980
and invites you to her mansion for a chat.

541
00:27:26,590 --> 00:27:27,400
All right.

542
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:30,090
I will definitely be there on time.

543
00:27:30,790 --> 00:27:31,590
Zheng.

544
00:27:32,480 --> 00:27:33,740
Tomorrow is a good day.

545
00:27:33,880 --> 00:27:34,640
How about

546
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,880
you and Xiao Chi come with me?

547
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:38,550
Chu,

548
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:39,750
then...

549
00:27:42,880 --> 00:27:44,480
I think I'll pass.

550
00:27:45,400 --> 00:27:46,240
You know,

551
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:47,960
I just took office
in the Ministry of Rites,

552
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:50,160
and there are many matters to hand over.

553
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:51,790
I also have a lot of documents

554
00:27:51,790 --> 00:27:53,050
and case files to read.

555
00:27:53,400 --> 00:27:53,960
I...

556
00:27:54,830 --> 00:27:56,230
I think I'll just skip it.

557
00:27:59,750 --> 00:28:00,880
That's fine too.

558
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:02,920
Then I expect

559
00:28:03,550 --> 00:28:06,070
you to achieve something
in the Ministry of Rites

560
00:28:06,070 --> 00:28:08,880
by promoting etiquette in the court,

561
00:28:09,030 --> 00:28:10,830
to be an example for the ministers

562
00:28:10,830 --> 00:28:12,760
and a role model for all officials.

563
00:28:18,750 --> 00:28:19,440
I

564
00:28:19,750 --> 00:28:20,810
accept the decree.

565
00:28:47,440 --> 00:28:49,170
The Eldest Princess's person?

566
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:52,810
She left the palace secretly at this time.

567
00:29:08,270 --> 00:29:10,550
I've had amnesia for so many years.

568
00:29:10,550 --> 00:29:12,640
It won't be easy to recover my memory.

569
00:29:17,030 --> 00:29:18,640
There must be another way.

570
00:29:22,030 --> 00:29:22,880
Forget it.

571
00:29:25,880 --> 00:29:26,920
Things are fine

572
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:28,330
the way they are.

573
00:31:15,790 --> 00:31:17,030
General, His Majesty has an urgent matter

574
00:31:17,030 --> 00:31:17,880
and summons you back to the palace.
